WEBVTT

00:12:59.793 --> 00:13:04.557
and every month she goes
to the Western Union office

00:13:04.581 --> 00:13:06.120
with some cash

00:13:06.144 --> 00:13:09.104
to send her remittances
to her mom in Manila.

00:13:09.835 --> 00:13:11.728
It costs her around 10 percent;

00:13:11.752 --> 00:13:13.992
the money takes four to seven
days to get there;

00:13:14.016 --> 00:13:16.180
her mom never knows
when it's going to arrive.

00:13:16.204 --> 00:13:18.738
It takes five hours
out of her week to do this.

00:13:19.571 --> 00:13:20.723
Six months ago,

00:13:20.747 --> 00:13:25.327
Analie Domingo used
a blockchain application called Abra.

00:13:25.771 --> 00:13:28.384
And from her mobile device,
she sent 300 bucks.

00:13:28.408 --> 00:13:30.888
It went directly
to her mom's mobile device